{"title_page": "Fabien Barrillon", "text_new": "{{short description|French professional footballer|bot=PearBOT 5}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Fabien Barrillon\n| fullname = \n| image = \n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1988|4|9|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[Aubagne]], France\n| death_date = \n| death_place = \n| position = [[Defender (association football)|Centre back]]\n| height = 1.81 m\n| currentclub = [[Marignane Gignac F.C.|Marignane Gignac]]\n| clubnumber = 29\n| youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = [[Olympique de Marseille|Marseille]]\n| years1 = 2006\u20132009 | clubs1 = [[Olympique de Marseille|Marseille B]] | caps1 =     | goals1 = \n| years2 = 2009\u20132010 | clubs2 = [[SO Cassis Carnoux|Cassis Carnoux]]   | caps2 = 23  | goals2 = 0\n| years3 = 2010\u20132014 | clubs3 = [[FC Istres|Istres]]                   | caps3 = 111 | goals3 = 6\n| years4 = 2014\u20132016 | clubs4 = [[N\u00eemes Olympique|N\u00eemes]]              | caps4 = 46  | goals4 = 3\n| years5 = 2016      | clubs5 = [[US Cr\u00e9teil-Lusitanos|US Cr\u00e9teil]]    | caps5 = 10   | goals5 = 0\n| years6 = 2016\u20132018 | clubs6 = [[GS Consolat]]                        | caps6 = 54   | goals6 = 3\n| years7 = 2018\u20132019 | clubs7 = [[Annecy FC|Annecy]]                   | caps7 = 11   | goals7 = 1\n| years8 = 2019\u2013     | clubs8 = [[Marignane Gignac F.C.|Marignane Gignac]]   | caps8 = 10  | goals8 = 0\n| pcupdate = 20:53, 19 January 2020 (UTC)\n}}\n\n'''Fabien Barrillon''' (born 9 April 1988) is a French professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]] for [[Marignane Gignac F.C.|Marignane Gignac]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ledauphine.com/sport/2018/06/09/barrillon-(annecy)-xx|title=Barrillon (Annecy) : \" Annecy n'est pas un club de N2 \"|date=9 June 2018|website=ledauphine.com|access-date=30 October 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Club career==\nBarrillon began his career as a youth player for [[Olympique de Marseille]]. After several seasons playing for Marseille's reserve team, he joined [[SO Cassis Carnoux|Cassis Carnoux]] in 2009. The upcoming year he was transferred to [[FC Istres|Istres]], which he also [[Captain (association football)|captained]], spending four years there. In June 2014, he was about to sign with [[Romania]]n side [[FC Petrolul Ploie\u0219ti|Petrolul Ploie\u0219ti]], moving abroad for the first time, but after it was discovered that he had some medical problems, the transfer broke down.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fcpetrolul.ro/ro/Petrolul-a-renuntat-la-Fabien-Barrillon/ |title=Petrolul a renun\u021bat la Fabien Barrillon |date=24 June 2014 |language=Romanian |publisher=[[FC Petrolul Ploie\u0219ti|Petrolul Ploie\u0219ti]] |access-date=24 June 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627074156/http://www.fcpetrolul.ro/ro/Petrolul-a-renuntat-la-Fabien-Barrillon/ |archive-date=27 June 2014 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\nIn June 2019, Barrillon joined [[Marignane Gignac F.C.|Marignane Gignac]].<ref>[http://www.actufoot.com/13/nouveau-challenge-fabien-barrillon/ NOUVEAU CHALLENGE POUR FABIEN BARRILLON !], actufoot.com, 25 June 2019</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Soccerway|fabien-barrillon/87569}}\n*{{FootballDatabase.eu|77021}}\n*[http://www.foot-national.com/6253-joueur-football-Barrillon-Fabien.html foot-national.com profile]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Barrillon, Fabien}}\n[[Category:1988 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Aubagne]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Bouches-du-Rh\u00f4ne]]\n[[Category:French footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n[[Category:Olympique de Marseille players]]\n[[Category:SO Cassis Carnoux players]]\n[[Category:FC Istres players]]\n[[Category:N\u00eemes Olympique players]]\n[[Category:US Cr\u00e9teil-Lusitanos players]]\n[[Category:GS Consolat players]]\n[[Category:Annecy FC players]]\n[[Category:Marignane Gignac F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Ligue 2 players]]\n[[Category:Championnat National players]]\n\n\n{{France-footy-defender-1980s-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|French professional footballer|bot=PearBOT 5}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name      = Fabien Barrillon\n| fullname = \n| image = \n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1988|4|9|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[Aubagne]], France\n| death_date = \n| death_place = \n| position = [[Defender (association football)|Centre back]]\n| height = 1.81 m\n| currentclub = [[Marignane Gignac F.C.|Marignane Gignac]]\n| clubnumber = 29\n| youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = [[Olympique de Marseille|Marseille]]\n| years1 = 2006\u20132009 | clubs1 = [[Olympique de Marseille|Marseille B]] | caps1 =     | goals1 = \n| years2 = 2009\u20132010 | clubs2 = [[SO Cassis Carnoux|Cassis Carnoux]]   | caps2 = 23  | goals2 = 0\n| years3 = 2010\u20132014 | clubs3 = [[FC Istres|Istres]]                   | caps3 = 111 | goals3 = 6\n| years4 = 2014\u20132016 | clubs4 = [[N\u00eemes Olympique|N\u00eemes]]              | caps4 = 46  | goals4 = 3\n| years5 = 2016      | clubs5 = [[US Cr\u00e9teil-Lusitanos|US Cr\u00e9teil]]    | caps5 = 10   | goals5 = 0\n| years6 = 2016\u20132018 | clubs6 = [[GS Consolat]]                        | caps6 = 54   | goals6 = 3\n| years7 = 2018\u20132019 | clubs7 = [[Annecy FC|Annecy]]                   | caps7 = 11   | goals7 = 1\n| years8 = 2019\u2013     | clubs8 = [[Marignane Gignac F.C.|Marignane Gignac]]   | caps8 = 10  | goals8 = 0\n| pcupdate = 20:53, 19 January 2020 (UTC)\n}}\n\n'''Fabien Barrillon''' (born 9 April 1988) is a [[France|French]] professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]] for [[Marignane Gignac F.C.|Marignane Gignac]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ledauphine.com/sport/2018/06/09/barrillon-(annecy)-xx|title=Barrillon (Annecy) : \" Annecy n'est pas un club de N2 \"|date=9 June 2018|website=ledauphine.com|access-date=30 October 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Club career==\nBarrillon began his career as a youth player for [[Olympique de Marseille]]. After several seasons playing for Marseille's reserve team, he joined [[SO Cassis Carnoux|Cassis Carnoux]] in 2009. The upcoming year he was transferred to [[FC Istres|Istres]], which he also [[Captain (association football)|captained]], spending four years there. In June 2014, he was about to sign with [[Romania]]n side [[FC Petrolul Ploie\u0219ti|Petrolul Ploie\u0219ti]], moving abroad for the first time, but after it was discovered that he had some medical problems, the transfer broke down.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fcpetrolul.ro/ro/Petrolul-a-renuntat-la-Fabien-Barrillon/ |title=Petrolul a renun\u021bat la Fabien Barrillon |date=June 24, 2014 |language=Romanian |publisher=[[FC Petrolul Ploie\u0219ti|Petrolul Ploie\u0219ti]] |access-date=June 24, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627074156/http://www.fcpetrolul.ro/ro/Petrolul-a-renuntat-la-Fabien-Barrillon/ |archive-date=June 27, 2014 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\nIn June 2019, Barrillon joined [[Marignane Gignac F.C.|Marignane Gignac]].<ref>[http://www.actufoot.com/13/nouveau-challenge-fabien-barrillon/ NOUVEAU CHALLENGE POUR FABIEN BARRILLON !], actufoot.com, 25 June 2019</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Soccerway|fabien-barrillon/87569}}\n*{{FootballDatabase.eu|77021}}\n*[http://www.foot-national.com/6253-joueur-football-Barrillon-Fabien.html foot-national.com profile]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Barrillon, Fabien}}\n[[Category:1988 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Aubagne]]\n[[Category:French footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n[[Category:Olympique de Marseille players]]\n[[Category:SO Cassis Carnoux players]]\n[[Category:FC Istres players]]\n[[Category:N\u00eemes Olympique players]]\n[[Category:US Cr\u00e9teil-Lusitanos players]]\n[[Category:GS Consolat players]]\n[[Category:Annecy FC players]]\n[[Category:Marignane Gignac F.C. 